k you!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "9e3d8cde-a635-0ffb-a5db-b1df29517da8"], "hdd974154ga1b1g46bdgbd3fg46a8035daeca": ["Get out of my sight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "7e5eaa26-5237-adbc-3100-063eb80885a0"], "h7dab46efg5bd5g43c1gbd21gad5438b1b14a": ["<i>Observe her silently. Maybe these are just crocodile tears.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "99718224-6911-02b7-e5c3-e0e42caee662"], "hc3c00e5fg29efg455fga1f3g349de1b5f4fc": ["*You notice she's trembling. The tears streaming down her cheeks are indeed real.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "663bba17-8915-a161-ecce-9c68fbf25a5c"], "h37f0ee2bgce54g4362gbcc7g08d3bae74359": ["<i>Lunge at her. Real tears or not, she tried to rob you.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "672a360c-c212-c196-8450-1e0e02e215dd"], "h45fef8f1g21d8g435aga477g2e88be8948a0": ["*Her hands hides her face, preventing you from reading her expression.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "984ca6e2-ef29-01fa-24bd-bb40c3b25344"], "h6c991903g2eb9g4799g88bcg57cccdbc421d": ["<i>Ignore her theatrics and grab her.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "384728f2-e5b3-90a4-4983-0b2e0cd5594b"], "h4360c3ecg277eg4afeg9cf6g75dad1c2b9fd": ["Aah! Let go of me!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "06339d92-9cff-5c5c-a36f-a115cd0592e5"], "h0b6eafbbgd5a7g4aaagb7a3g54975911467c": ["Help!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_CaughtThief.html", "376c4f4c-251d-1916-8308-a77c0ee339fd"], "h2aafab2agbbceg416fgb03dg7ce356d51306": ["Help!", "540ddc1f-42c